'''Formex''' was a [[Polymer/Legends|polymer]]ic construction material used to build a variety of architectural designs, including columns and roadways. As a fluid, it could be poured into castings on site and manipulated to form various shapes and structures.<ref name="GSWU" /> Formex was commonly used in buildings, including those found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Etti IV]],<ref name="HSE" /> in [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan's]] [[Spaceport Southeast II]] area,<ref name="HSR">''[[Han Solo's Revenge]]''</ref> on [[Harridan (planet)|Harridan]],<ref name="C41">{{ChallengeCite|41|Paid in Full}}</ref> in [[Vandalar City]] on [[Reaper's World/Legends|Reaper's World]], in [[Kavila]] on [[Dalos IV]],<ref name="E">{{WEGCite|story=Elusive (adventure)|book=No Disintegrations (West End Games)}}</ref> and as support structures and floors in [[Mesa 291]] on [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]].<ref name="RB">{{WEGCite|story=Rebel Breakout|book=Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game (first edition)}}</ref> Shaped formex and [[Permacite/Legends|permacite]] were commonly used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] as building materials for their outposts.<ref name="SWS">''[[The Star Wars Sourcebook]]''</ref>

